- cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science): The paper discusses constraints over strings, which is a topic related to logic in computer science. 
- cs.SE (Software Engineering): The paper mentions real-world applications such as software analysis and verification, testing, and web security. 
- cs.FL (Formal Languages and Automata Theory): The paper deals with string variables and constraints, which are related to formal languages and automata theory. 
- cs.CR (Cryptography and Security): The paper mentions web security as one of the real-world applications of string constraints.
